{"tid":1403550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在此感謝何君堯，警察","createTime":"2019-08-03T19:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T19:45:29.000Z","uid":250462,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b81c1cb7c85036cab738b882de0e80afc82114db","tid":1403550,"uid":250462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:42:40.000Z","msg":"係何君堯教識我地咩叫先撩者賤，藍絲郁手，義士還拖，天公地義。<br />\n係克警教識我地以和平對住佢地同政府係冇用，多謝佢地令廣大市民懂得提升武力以達致以武制暴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dccf78c0403bfcc44214a85ea46e1348776e96","tid":1403550,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:44:58.000Z","msg":"多謝佢令我知道警察即係黑社會，以後為民除害不必留手"},{"pid":"c3b317cf9ee7b5e32f4a26de709f9d5776127011","tid":1403550,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">毫無人格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></span></blockquote>"}]}